WEBVTT

00:08.000 --> 00:11.125
Oh, for shit's sake.
Again?

00:11.125 --> 00:14.542
The fuck is going on
that's so important

00:14.542 --> 00:15.417
you're missing our episodes?

00:15.417 --> 00:18.667
You should look
into that, buster.

00:18.667 --> 00:20.709
Okay, here it is.

00:20.709 --> 00:22.500
[Fiona]  Everyone is late
with their rent.

00:22.500 --> 00:24.333
Evict her ass.

00:24.333 --> 00:26.709
You fucked
with the wrong girl!

00:26.709 --> 00:28.500
You are about to witness
the rebirth

00:28.500 --> 00:30.458
of a proactive
member of society.

00:30.458 --> 00:32.500
[Adeeb] I am impressed
by your work ethic

00:32.500 --> 00:33.750
and your dedication.
That's why

00:33.750 --> 00:34.834
I'm making you supervisor.

00:34.834 --> 00:37.834
- [Adeeb laughing]
- Okay.

00:37.834 --> 00:40.500
Who are you talking to?

00:40.500 --> 00:42.375
[Debbie]  It's just
my stupid boyfriend.

00:42.375 --> 00:43.375
Wants me to give him
a sponge bath every night.

00:43.375 --> 00:45.834
- [Debbie] He's paraplegic.
- I'll do it.

00:45.834 --> 00:48.208
I need a new patient
for my practicum hours.

00:48.208 --> 00:50.375
Immigration!
Nobody move!

00:50.375 --> 00:51.875
What the hell is going on?

00:51.875 --> 00:53.542
That's her.
She's the leader.

00:53.542 --> 00:55.542
