00:59.500 --> 01:01.333
[Lip] Thanks for the rehab.

01:01.333 --> 01:03.542
[Parminder]  I biposied
your lump, Mr. Ball.

01:03.542 --> 01:05.709
- It's benign.
- I don't have cancer!

01:05.709 --> 01:07.583
[cheering]

01:07.583 --> 01:09.166
[Fiona] Frank found
seven pounds of meth

01:09.166 --> 01:10.875
that Monica had,
and it's getting flushed

01:10.875 --> 01:12.542
- down the toilet.
- [Frank] Nobody flushes

01:12.542 --> 01:15.959
70,000 dollars' worth
of maternal bequest

01:15.959 --> 01:17.750
down the drain.

01:17.750 --> 01:19.917
So, you're the little fuckers
who stole my meth.

01:19.917 --> 01:20.834
- [Ian] Uh, crap.
- [Eric] Shit!

01:20.834 --> 01:24.417
Where's my fucking meth?

